<p>
<note n="0302001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0302001">【原】宣德四年刊德富蘇峯氏藏本，【甲】崇禎十七年刊增上寺藏本，此序依甲本載之</note>
<note n="0303001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303001">蘆字前行甲本有廬山蓮宗寶鑑念佛正因卷第一十三字</note>
<note n="0303002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303002">光＝增【甲】</note>
<note n="0303003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303003">白蓮之教＝蓮宗之旨【甲】</note>
<note n="0303004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303004"><g ref="#CB05277">䉜</g>＝薙【甲】</note>
<note n="0304001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0304001">白蓮＝蓮宗【甲】</note>
<note n="0304002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0304002">賜白＝勅明【甲】</note>
<note n="0304003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0304003">白蓮宗主＝蓮社正宗【甲】</note>
<note n="0304004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0304004">〔白〕－【甲】</note>
<note n="0305001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0305001">辨＝辯【甲】</note>
